Privacy Policy for BloomUp

Effective Date: 24 October 2025

BloomUp ("we", "our", or "us") operates as a mobile game available on Google Play.
This Privacy Policy describes how we handle information when you use our game.

1. Information We Do Not Collect

BloomUp does not collect, store, or share any personal data from users.
We do not request or access any information such as:

Personal identifiers (name, email, phone number)

Device or location data

Usage analytics or crash reports

Your gameplay data is stored locally on your device and is never transmitted to us or any third party.

2. No Third-Party Services

BloomUp does not use any third-party services such as analytics providers, advertising networks, or cloud databases.

